VERSION 3.0.3                                                         XX XX XXXX
New:
    * Ability to refresh minimodules via Ajax                               -OLI
    * Implemented this for RER, News and XRay                               -OLI
    * Ajax refresh is done (at max) every 2 minutes                         -OLI
    * Added bottom pagination to the TOL                                    -OLI
Bug:
    * Fix wrong minimodules fetching when added via ajax                    -OLI
    * Fix Pix minimodule not working                                        -OLI
================================================================================
VERSION 3.0.2                                                         04 11 2012

New:
    * Add tests for Collection class                                        -IOS
    * Change favicon                                                        -IOS
    * Introduce foreign keys and fix some insert() functions                -IOS
    * Use Yahoo Weather API, since Google Weather is gone                   -IOS
    * New import scripts, for Sup'Op (IOGS) and ENSTA                       -IOS
    * Improve DB migration script to remove sensible data                   -IOS
    * Room management for groups                                            -IOS
    * Add more magic in Meta class (has, collection and from functions)     -IOS

Remove:
    * Remove MySQL backup system (now external)                             -IOS
    * Remove survey module                                                  -IOS
    * Drop ancient tables                                                   -IOS

Bug:
    * Fix wrong implementation of Collection::has                           -IOS
    * Fix 0-promotion case handling in birthday minimodule                  -IOS
    * Revoke public visibility of some pages                            -IOS/PAD
    * Fix fromID string-number comparaison                                  -GUI
    * Hide 0000-00-00 birthday                                              -IOS
    * Use membre caste instead of the restricted in TOL searches            -IOS

================================================================================
