VERSION 3.0.0                                                         28 02 2011

First stage of the development to Frankiz3            -MAT/RIT/BRI/FEA/PJ/QT/XEL

New comparing to Frankiz 2:

    * Database model with Schema/Meta/Select
    * Collection class
    * Users can be friend, member or admin of a group
    * Use Less to generate CSS

From Frankiz 2:

    * Minimodules
    * TOL (Trombi On Line)

